# Delta Web — production env example.
# Vite bakes VITE_* into the bundle at BUILD time, not runtime. These
# get set in Render's dashboard (or render.yaml) before `npm run build`
# runs on Render.
#
# Render reads them as build-time env vars when the static site builds.
# Do not commit a real .env.production with values to git.

